We've given dialogue starting elements a custom element attribute:

tag: dialogue_start

This way, the game engine knows where to look for each NPC's dialogue start.

We've used this solution in the Unreal Engine demo game.

Right click the element and choose "Properties," to see it.

dialogue: end
